Stuart Randall (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stuart_Randall_(actor) 0 Stuart Randall (born Clarence Maxwell, July 24, 1909 – June 22, 1988) was an American actor of film and television who appeared on screen between 1950 and 1971.
